    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "49ers\nClementine",
      "Menu\nTUCSON • SAN FRANCISCO\nWelcome\nAboard!\nLunch\nSAN FRANCISCO\nSeafood Cocktail\nBroiled New York Steak Bordelaise\nButtered Peas\nAu Gratin Potatoes\nLuncheon Rolls\n'49ers and guests\nChef's Salad Jardiniere\nChocolate Cake\nAll of us at Pan American wish you the\nbest of luck in your bid for the championship\nthis season. As \"Goal Rushers\" and fans of\nlong standing, we'll be following every play.\nWe appreciate this opportunity to serve you\non your special charter flight — everything is\nbeing done to make it the most enjoyable ever.\nOnce again, welcome aboard and good luck!\nAssorted Cheese Tray\nCoffee\nTea\nMilk\nMixed Nuts Mint Wafers\nFruit Bowl\nPAN AMERICAN WORLD AIRWAYS"
    ],
